      </div>
      <div class="card-body open">
        <div class="table-wrap"><table>
          <tr><th>為替変動</th><th>輸出</th><th>輸入</th><th>海外旅行</th></tr>
          <tr><td><strong>円高（例:1ドル100円→80円）</strong></td><td>不利（価格↑）</td><td>有利（価格↓）</td><td>有利（購買力↑）</td></tr>
          <tr><td><strong>円安（例:1ドル100円→130円）</strong></td><td>有利（価格↓）</td><td>不利（価格↑）</td><td>不利（購買力↓）</td></tr>
        </table></div>
        <div class="point-box">
